{"posts":{"4":{"id":0,"title":"从开始处开始","date":"2013-06-16T08:36:37.000Z","updated":"2013-08-23T14:44:24.000Z","categories":[],"tags":[],"comments":true,"layout":"post","content":"<p>从开始寻找一个好用的协作工具 到今天一到办公室立刻打开亲手打造的teambition 很多事情变得不同</p>\n<p>来到新的办公室 每一天都变得更加出色 也不断迎来新的成员</p>\n<p>交了新的朋友 有了越来越多的合作伙伴 也不断萌发新的想法</p>\n<p>每一天 都有新的企业开始使用teambition进行协同工作</p>\n<h2>这些改变 让我们希望作出改变</h2>\n<p>不知从那一天起 我们开始频繁地进出讨论室</p>\n<p>记得曾经在某个公开演讲上说 teambition团队众人皆为设计师 这句话 如果回顾过去的几个月 那么实在是过于真实的写照 我们消耗设计本和绘图笔的速度实在是过于惊人</p>\n<p>不知是多少个小时之后 我们找到了答案</p>\n<h2>回到开始</h2>\n<p>teambition好用 是因为我们本就是为了自己使用而打造他</p>\n<p>所以 所谓改变 其出发点</p>\n<p>不会是满世界的产品经理嚷嚷的以用户为中心</p>\n<p>不会是满世界的CEO叫嚣的抛开KPI</p>\n<h2>而是 如果让我想象 我可以如何工作</h2>\n<p>着手一个项目时，可以轻轻松松地了解所有进展</p>\n<p>在办公桌前坐下，就知道我应该开始干什么</p>\n<p>拿到手的文件永远是最新版本</p>\n<p>工作环境 可人 舒适 而 优雅</p>\n<p>...</p>\n<h2>我们正日以继夜地打造那个 从开始我们就想像拥有的teambition</h2>\n<h2>请期待</h2>\n","excerpt":0,"source":"_posts/1.md","slug":"1","ctime":"2013-08-23T14:47:15.000Z","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:44:24.000Z","author":"俊元"},"_primary":5},"pages":{"_primary":1},"categories":{"_primary":1},"tags":{"_primary":1},"assets":{"1":{"source":"themes/light/source/js/gallery.js","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"2":{"source":"themes/light/source/js/jquery.imagesloaded.min.js","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"3":{"source":"themes/light/source/js/moment.min.js","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"4":{"source":"themes/light/source/js/twitter.js","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"5":{"source":"themes/light/source/fancybox/blank.gif","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"6":{"source":"themes/light/source/fancybox/fancybox_loading.gif","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"7":{"source":"themes/light/source/fancybox/fancybox_overlay.png","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"8":{"source":"themes/light/source/fancybox/fancybox_sprite.png","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"9":{"source":"themes/light/source/fancybox/jquery.fancybox.css","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"10":{"source":"themes/light/source/fancybox/jquery.fancybox.pack.js","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"11":{"source":"themes/light/source/css/style.styl","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"12":{"source":"themes/light/source/css/font/fontawesome-webfont.eot","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"13":{"source":"themes/light/source/css/font/fontawesome-webfont.svg","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"14":{"source":"themes/light/source/css/font/fontawesome-webfont.ttf","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"15":{"source":"themes/light/source/css/font/fontawesome-webfont.woff","mtime":"2013-08-23T14:23:17.000Z"},"_primary":16}}